<translation id="8453117565092476964">Ingobo yomlando yesifaki yonakele noma ayivumelekile. Sicela ulande futhi i-GTx Browser.</translation>
<translation id="8458614432758743027">I-GTx Browser idinga i-Windows 7 noma ngaphezulu.</translation>
<translation id="8463672209299734063">Ongakukhetha: Siza ekuthuthukiseni izakhi nokusebenza kwe-GTx BrowserOS ngokuthumela ngokuzenzekelayo idatha yokusetshenziswa neyokuxilonga ku-Google.</translation>
<translation id="8493179195440786826">I-GTx Browser ayikho kudethi</translation>
<translation id="8550334526674375523">Le phrofayela yomsebenzi ihluke ngokugcwele kusukela kuphrofayela yakho siqu.</translation>
<translation id="8558383651099478961">Umzali wakho uvale "Izimvume zamasayithi, izinhlelo zokusebenza, nezandiso" ze-GTx Browser. Ukwengeza le <ph name="EXTENSION_TYPE_PARAMETER" /> akuvumelekile.</translation>
