<translation id="8608079656141766906"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />Indlela esisebenzisa ngayo le datha:<ph name="END_BOLD" /> Amasayithi angagcina ulwazi nge-GTx Browser mayelana nezintshisekelo zakho. Ngokwesibonelo, uma uvakashela isayithi ukuze uthenge izicathulo zomjaho webanga elide, isayithi lingachaza intshisekelo yakho njengokugijima umjaho. Kamuva, uma uvakashela isayithi elihlukile ukuze ubhalisele umjaho, lelo sayithi lingakubonisa isikhangiso sezicathulo zokugijima ezisekelwe kuzintshisekelo zakho.</translation>
