<translation id="9106612006984859720">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-GTx Browser, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 8.1.</translation>
<translation id="91086099826398415">Vula isixhumanisi ku&amp;thebhu entsha ye-GTx Browser</translation>
<translation id="911206726377975832">Phinda ususe idatha yakho yokudlulisa amehlo?</translation>
<translation id="9144490074902256427">Phakathi nezivivinyo, ungakwazi ukubona nokususa izihloko onentshisekelo kuzo ezisetshenziswa amasayithi ukuze uboniswe izikhangiso. I-GTx Browser izolinganisa intshisekelo yakho ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wakamuva wokubhrawuza.</translation>
<translation id="9158494823179993217">Umlawuli wesistimu yakho ulungise i-GTx Browser ukuthi ivule esinye isiphequluli ukufinyelela i-<ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME" />.</translation>
